metadata.name: Block Quest PassKey #1/50
metadata.description:
This Block Quest PassKey allows entry to the token gated "Area 24" of Flagship

Add this NFT in your wallet connected to your Spatial.io account.

Enter Flagship Area-24 at this link

https://www.spatial.io/s/FLAGSHIP-Area24-62d71e3292d40100010c1c14

This is not the world you know. This is a mirror world. It looks and feels like a Flagship floor level. Perhaps you've even been there before. But it's not where you have ever ventured. You may find there is more to see in where you can't see... the night here lasts and lasts. But its easier to see what's in front of you when it's right in front of you. 

The location of PassKey#5 will take you back to the beginning. If you know your history, maybe you don't even need to be here. Then again, you may miss the piece you needed. It's always your choice though.  

Good Luck. etherstu
